And the people saying that she isn’t the same or is just doing it for the money or that her videos are getting boring, you must not have ever watch any other video of hers or are even a fan genuinely. She is literally always herself in her videos always, and I had fun watching this video because I enjoy her personality because she literally is just like me and it’s nice to see someone make it just by being themselves and gives me hope that I don’t have to feel like I’m a waste of space because of the way I am. If Emma can be successful by being herself, anyone can and I can. Obviously you can make YouTube videos for fun and money. That’s what I wanna do. Make money by doing something fun and that I genuinely enjoy and if I can make people happy and entertain and also get paid for it, that’s a great life. And I’m gonna give her that extra thumbs up, even if it doesn’t make any difference to the video, if you ever read this Emma, I really liked the video regardless because I think You as a person is fun to watch and it’s enough for me. I’m sorry that you felt like you had to do something to yourself that you didn’t want to do to make everyone else happy. I know exactly what that feels like and I hate that you ever had to feel it too
